OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA few coastal showers but
OL,6,Fgenerally a dry start with some good
OL,7,Fspells of sunshine. However showers
OL,8,Fdevelop more widely this morning,
OL,9,Falthough lighter and less frequent
OL,10,Fthan recent days. Northwesterly
OL,11,Fbreeze, strong at times near coast.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FSome late sunny spells and a
OL,14,Ffew showers this evening. Then dry
OL,15,Fovernight with long clear spells
OL,16,Fdeveloping. Touch of frost possible in
OL,17,Fsheltered spots. Winds easing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
