OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FA dry and largely sunny start,
OL,6,Fsome cloud will develop for the
OL,7,Fafternoon but it will remain dry.
OL,8,FNorthwesterly breeze continuing to
OL,9,Fease.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FDry
OL,12,Fmorning with sunny spells Saturday,
OL,13,Fbut cloud increasing with some rain
OL,14,Flater. Rain clearing overnight then
OL,15,Fsunny spells and a few showers. Rather
OL,16,Fcloudy Monday with occasional rain.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
